headline: Northrop Grumman: Mounting Challenges May Continue To Weigh On The Stock
summary: Northrop Grumman faces challenges from cost overruns on the Sentinel missile program, B-21 Raider losses, and a missed $30B contract. See why NOC stock is a Hold.
